    <div data-cid="1011892">
        <div class="main review-item" id="1011892">

            
    
    <header class="main-hd">
        <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/easyforget/" class="avator">
            <img width="24" height="24" src="https://img1.doubanio.com/icon/u1019347-8.jpg">
        </a>

        <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/easyforget/" class="name">吴昊桐</a>

            <span class="allstar40 main-title-rating" title="推荐"></span>

        <span content="2005-11-22" class="main-meta">2005-11-22 21:11:13</span>


    </header>


            <div class="main-bd">

                <h2><a href="https://book.douban.com/review/1011892/">以梦为生的女子</a></h2>

                <div id="review_1011892_short" class="review-short" data-rid="1011892">
                    <div class="short-content">

                        看了三毛所有的书，觉得她的性格很双重，她一生的悲剧在于太浪漫。但是很执着，我就要一生向着浪漫去，去的无所畏惧，立场决不动摇。她的书中很多避弃了自己苦难的历程。毕竟描述梦境是美丽的，甚至她自己也分不大清自己究竟是生活在梦里还是梦外了。她的勇敢完全是对自己真正...

                        &nbsp;(<a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-1011892-copy" class="unfold" title="展开">展开</a>)
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div id="review_1011892_full" class="hidden">
                    <div id="review_1011892_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
                </div>

                <div class="action">
                    <a href="javascript:;" class="action-btn up" data-rid="1011892" title="有用">
                        <img src="https://img1.doubanio.com/f/zerkalo/536fd337139250b5fb3cf9e79cb65c6193f8b20b/pics/up.png" />
                        <span id="r-useful_count-1011892">
                                148
                        </span>
                    </a>
                    <a href="javascript:;" class="action-btn down" data-rid="1011892" title="没用">
                        <img src="https://img1.doubanio.com/f/zerkalo/68849027911140623cf338c9845893c4566db851/pics/down.png" />
                        <span id="r-useless_count-1011892">
                                7
                        </span>
                    </a>
                    <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/1011892/#comments" class="reply ">61回应</a>

                    <a href="javascript:;;" class="fold hidden">收起</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

            
    
    <div data-cid="1132025">
        <div class="main review-item" id="1132025">

            
    
    <header class="main-hd">
        <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/wy2004/" class="avator">
